keyMappings:
map R reload hard
map M toggleMuteTab all
map q createTab https://www.youtube.com/
map e createTab https://www.github.com/
map w createTab https://chromewebstore.google.com/
map ct LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text

# Custom Searches
map s1 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=wi
map s2 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=go
map s3 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=ye
map s4 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=gm
map s5 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=du
map s6 Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=az
searchEngines:
wi: https://www.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special:Search&search=%s Wikipedia
go: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
ye: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
gm: https://www.google.com/maps?q=%s Google maps
du: https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%s DuckDuckGo
az: https://www.amazon.com/s/?field-keywords=%s

# l: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s&btnI I'm feeling lucky...
# bi: https://www.bing.com/search?q=%s Bing
